name: Invesco US Treasury Floating Rate Note Index ETF (USD)
longDescription: In order to achieve its investment objectives, IUFR currently holds the Constituent Securities of the FTSE US Treasury Floating-Rate Note Index in approximately the same proportion as they are reflected in that Index and may use, at the discretion of Invesco Capital, the sampling methodology described in the prospectus. Additional investment strategies that IUFR may use are described under the heading Investment Strategies. The ETF invests, directly or indirectly, primarily in US Treasury floating rate notes with timetomaturity greater than or equal to one month.
